{"type": "article", "id": 19419, "title": "厨房漏水工具", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-21T07:40:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021151458hY0Uw7ORTqZKiXs.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一套放在厨房水槽里的漏水工具，像杯子一样的容器下面有漏孔，帮助清洗蔬果的同时就把用过的水漏下去，也将剩余的渣滓留在其中，方便倾倒。不用的时候，它就是一个装厨房工具的收纳盒，或者搜集肥皂泡来清洗水池。此外，它还带有一个加宽的漏斗，更方便将切菜板上的蔬果收进容器里。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145919sLOGfVbZji3vlPyh.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"425\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65384615\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145919F7oCdxRzWe8Lr0VM.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"714\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145920NYnAlzq3ebfkVXLv.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"840\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145921uLHKvSwmcJkdReAa.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"698\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}